#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:16
msgid ""
"**Easy customization:** We have provided the following customization "
"variables at the top of the script you can set to your liking:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:19
msgid ""
"**faderStart**: If set to *true*, it allows decks to start when their "
"channel or the cross-fader is opened. (This is also toggleable with the "
"topmost button on the controller. See below.)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:22
msgid ""
"**scratchFactor**: Adjusts the speed of scratching with the select knob. "
"(Defaults to **2**.)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:25
msgid ""
"Just open the ``controllers/Stanton-SCS1m-scripts.js`` file in your favorite"
" text editor (Wordpad works too) and you’ll see these variables right near "
"the top. Edit & save."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:29
msgid "Deck controls"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:32
#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:70
msgid "*Refer to the image above, top to bottom*"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:34
msgid ""
"**a** buttons: Sync function: change the pitch of the deck so that its BPM "
"matches that of the other deck (assuming the pitch range is sufficient)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:36
msgid "**b** buttons: Toggle headphone cue"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:37
msgid "**Gain, High, Mid, Low** knobs: as labeled"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:38
msgid "**Pan** knob: *unused*"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:39
msgid "**c** encoders"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:40
msgid "Rotate to increase or decrease the pitch range in 1% steps"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:41
msgid "Press to toggle the flange effect"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:42
msgid ""
"**c** displays: Show the current pitch adjustment percentage. The back light"
" color changes with the pitch range:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:44
msgid "Green = 1%-25%"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:45
msgid "Orange = 25%-50%"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:46
msgid "Red = 50% and above"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:47
msgid "**c** A buttons: Permanently lower the pitch by 1%"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:48
msgid "**c** B buttons: Permanently raise the pitch by 1%"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:49
msgid "**e** sliders: Pitch adjust"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:50
msgid ""
"**e** buttons: Temporarily raise the pitch by 4% for as long as held (pitch "
"bend up.)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:52
msgid ""
"**g** buttons: Temporarily lower the pitch by 4% for as long as held (pitch "
"bend down.)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:54
msgid "**d** encoders"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:55
msgid ""
"Rotate to nudge the track either direction (akin to twisting a record "
"spindle)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:57
msgid "Press to toggle reverse playback"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:58
msgid "LEDs show current track position"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:59
msgid ""
"**d** displays: Show the current track time remaining. They will flash "
"slowly when less than 30 seconds remain, quickly when less than 15 seconds "
"remain."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:61
msgid "**d** A buttons: Rewind"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:62
msgid "**d** B buttons: Fast-forward"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:63
msgid "**f** sliders: Volume adjust"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:64
msgid "**f** buttons: Play/pause"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:65
msgid "**h** buttons: Cue"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:67
msgid "Global controls"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:72
msgid "**z** button: Toggle fader start/cue"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:73
msgid "**Master, Headphones, Cue Mix** knobs: as labeled"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:74
msgid "**Zone** knob: *unused*"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:75
msgid "**Gain** knob: *unused*"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:76
msgid "**i** knob: Adjust flange effect depth"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:77
msgid "**j** knob: Adjust flange effect delay"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:78
msgid "**k** knob: Adjust flange effect period (Low Frequency Oscillator)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:79
msgid "**l** knob: Adjust main pan (balance)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:80
msgid "**p** button: *unused*"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:81
msgid "**m** button: BPM tap for Deck 1"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:82
msgid "**n** button: *unused*"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:83
msgid "**o** button: BPM tap for Deck 2"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:84
msgid ""
"**Preset** buttons: Hot cue points for the selected deck (**q** button)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:85
msgid ""
"**Bank Down** button: select backward between Library, Playlist, and Browse "
"views"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:87
msgid ""
"**Bank Up** button: select forward between Library, Playlist, and Browse "
"views"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:89
msgid ""
"**q** button: Change which deck’s hot cues are active (**Preset** buttons.) "
"Off is Deck 1, On (red) is Deck 2."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:91
msgid "**r** jog wheel:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:92
msgid "**Browse mode**:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:94
msgid "Rotate to move the track select highlight"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:95
msgid ""
"Press to load the selected track into the first stopped deck, if any. "
"//(This is [*not working*](https://github.com/mixxxdj/mixxx/issues/5815) in "
"1.9.x for some reason.)//"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:99
msgid "**Control mode**:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:101
msgid "Rotate to scratch the song on the selected deck"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:102
msgid "//Pressing does nothing//"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:104
msgid "**Cancel** button:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:105
msgid ""
"**Browse mode**: Press to load the highlighted song onto deck 1, if it’s not"
" currently playing."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:107
msgid "**Control mode**: hold down to enable scratching on deck 1"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:108
msgid "**Enter** button:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:109
msgid ""
"**Browse mode**: Press to load the highlighted song onto deck 2, if it’s not"
" currently playing."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:111
msgid "**Control mode**: hold down to enable scratching on deck 2"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:112
msgid ""
"//**Setup** button: unused by Mixxx but will enter the mixer’s internal "
"setup menu//"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:114
msgid "**Control** button: Selects scratching mode for the jog wheel"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/stanton_scs1m.md:115
msgid "**Browse** button: Selects track browse mode for the jog wheel"
msgstr ""

